// --- 1. REVIVES AND HEALING (Score 0: handled by the natural AI preset) ---
// Healing Fall: Jump to an open tile, then heal each adjacent unit; upgrade costs less.
// Healing Salve: You or an adjacent unit gains +1 Health Regen; upgrade gives +2.
// Existing regen only applies a small penalty so stackable sustain is still considered.
// Revive: Revive a body to 50% HP and cure one injury.
// Born Again: Revive a body to 100% HP and give it All Stats Up; base also puts you to sleep.
// Guardian Angel: Make a unit The Alpha; The Alpha gets +50% Dodge Chance. Upgrade gains infinite range and costs less.
// Reverse Damage: Reverse the last damage an adjacent unit took; upgrade works at range.
// Cleanse: Remove all debuffs from units in an area; upgrade grants Holy Shield per debuff removed.
