// --- 2. SPECIFIC BUFFS (Enemy check + duplicate check) ---
// Haste: Give +10 Speed until end of next turn; upgrade affects units in an area.
// Existing speed only applies a small penalty so haste can still be refreshed when useful.
// Divine Protection: Give a unit +1 Holy Shield and +1 Kinetic Spikes. That unit becomes The Alpha.
// Existing Shield only applies a small penalty so clerics can still stack protection when needed.
// Circle of Protection: Give nearby units +1 Holy Shield; upgrade also gives +1 Health Regen.
Haste.merge { damage_instance { ai_base_score 0 effects { Conditional_Speculative {  Conditional_HasStatus { status Haste FlatAIBonus -8 } } } } }
