// --- 3. GENERAL TEAM BUFFS (Enemy check only to save mana) ---
// Prayer: Heal units in an area; upgrade uses a larger area and infinite range.
// Buddy Up: Jump to an open tile next to an ally; upgrade costs less.
// Ethereal: Gain 4 Holy Shield, 3 Shield, heal 2 HP, and Brace 1.
// Benediction: Heal EVERYTHING for 2 HP; upgrade costs less.
// Crusade: You and your allies move toward the nearest enemy; upgrade also gives +1 Strength.
// Rally: Force a unit to attack one of its enemies; upgrade affects an area.
// Anoint: Give +2 diminishing Health Regen and random stat ups; upgrade increases targets/stats.
// Chosen Warrior: Buff a unit's Damage and mark it The Alpha; upgrade also grants Magic Damage and costs less.
// SwiftSanctify / Swift Servant: Give a unit +1 Bonus Move and make it The Alpha; upgraded version gains infinite range, costs less, and also gives you +1 Bonus Move when targeting the Alpha.
// Divine Gift: Gain All Stats Up; mana cost is reduced by HP healed this turn. Upgrade also gives +1 Holy Shield.
// Holy Weapon: Free once-per-turn dash attack whose range/damage/knockback scale with HP you healed this turn; upgrade doubles the scaling.
// Adoubement: Heal and cleanse a unit, then make it The Alpha with random stat ups; upgrade can also revive and grants more stats.
// Awaken: Revive a body to 1 HP; upgrade also gives Holy Shield and All Stats Up.
// Pray: Give another unit +5 Luck until the end of its next turn; upgrade swings Luck in an area for allies and enemies.
// Booster: Heal a unit; excess healing becomes random stat ups. Upgrade adds range.
// Stimulants: You and adjacent units gain +2 Speed; upgrade also gives +1 Intelligence.
// Existing speed/intel only applies a small penalty so the AI does not over-fixate on rebuffing.
// Grace: Apply a random positive effect; upgrade also heals and grants a random stat up.
