// --- 5. STRICT DEBUFFS (Nested anti-duplicate WITH Anti-Freeze + Anti-Ally) ---
// Open Wounds: Attack that deals more damage the lower the target's health percent; upgrade scales harder.
// Convert: Inflict Charm 2 on an adjacent unit; upgrade can permanently recruit low-health non-boss enemies.
// Turn Foe: Force a nearby unit to move away; upgrade also inflicts Madness 1 and Confusion 1 on enemies.
// Heretic Mark: Inflict Ostracized 2; upgrade increases it to Ostracized 4.
